variable.name: CTNI
variable.comment: Samples returned with 'ND' i.e. 'Not Detectable' were set to lower detectable limit of 0.69 pg/mL as indicated by CTNI_I. Use CTNI together with CTNI_I (measurable range indicator for CTNI) to determine cases within measurable range.

variable.name: CTNI_I
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for CTNI is 0.69 pg/mL. CTNI values below this limit were set to the lower detectable limit. Please use CTNI_I to see which records are below this limit.
